Titolo: Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire

Anno: 2018

Descrizione: Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire is a role-playing video game developed by Obsidian Entertainment and published by Versus Evil. It is the sequel to 2015's Pillars of Eternity, and was released for Microsoft Windows, Linux, macOS in May 2018, and for PlayStation 4, and Xbox One in January 2020. It will be released for the Nintendo Switch at a later date. The game was announced in January 2017 with a crowdfunding campaign on Fig, where it reached its funding goal within a day.

Genere: Role-playing 

Valutazione: 74
